AI in Excel typically falls into these categories:

Built-in AI Features

Ideas / Insights: Automatically analyzes your data to show trends, summaries, and visualizations.

Data Types & Smart Templates: Pulls live data (stocks, geography) and converts it into structured records.

Formulas & Functions

Advanced formulas for data manipulation, like:

TEXTJOIN, FILTER, UNIQUE, XLOOKUP, LET, LAMBDA

These let you automate patterns before applying AI.

AI-powered Add-ins & Integrations

Power Query + Power BI: AI transformations and predictive analytics.

Azure Machine Learning / OpenAI integration: For predictions, text analysis, or generating content.

GPT/LLM Add-ins: Use natural language to analyze or generate Excel data.
